---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
const { relativeClass = "" } = Astro.props;
---

<Section class={`${relativeClass}`}>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="py-6 md:py-10">

         
            <article class="text-lg text-slate-500" data-aos-id-testimonials="">

                <p class="mb-6 text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600">
                    The most valuable commodity in life and business today is <strong>TIME</strong>.
                </p>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Time lost can never be regained. So why do <strong>Recruitment Consultants</strong> and 
                    <strong>HR Professionals</strong> waste hours reviewing unsuitable CVs?  
                    Let’s be honest—**the “best CVs” don’t always mean the “best candidates.”**
                </p>
                
                <p class="mb-6 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800">
                    That changes now...
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    <strong>YourCVVideo.com Ltd</strong> is a revolutionary 
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">SaaS platform</span> designed for 
                    <strong>Recruitment Agencies</strong> and <strong>Hiring Companies</strong>.  
                    Our <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">AI-powered pre-screening tool</span> 
                    saves recruiters <strong>2-3 hours per day</strong>, streamlining the hiring process 
                    by eliminating time spent on unqualified CVs.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    <strong>Say goodbye to traditional written CVs</strong>—our cutting-edge platform introduces  
                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">video applications</span>, allowing candidates to 
                    showcase their skills and personality in a dynamic way.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    Our unique value lies in <strong>Human Intelligence + Artificial Intelligence</strong>,  
                    leveraging video functionality to enhance personal connections in recruitment.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    <strong>For Recruiters:</strong> Quickly view and assess candidates, focusing only on 
                    those with the right skills.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    <strong>For Candidates:</strong> Get noticed faster, demonstrate skills effectively, and 
                    increase job success rates with **CVVideos**.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    YourCVVideo is available for recruiters in  
                    <strong>UK, South Africa, Australia, New Zealand, India, Pakistan, Singapore, Hong Kong, UAE, 
                    and 23 European countries.</strong>
                </p>

                <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600">
                    Join the Recruitment Revolution Today!
                </p>

            </article>

            <!-- Call-to-Action Button -->
            <div class="text-center mt-8">
                <a href="browse-jobs"
                    class="btn text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 group transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out"
                    aria-label="Browse latest jobs">
                    Browse Latest Jobs 
                    <span class="tracking-normal text-blue-300 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 
                        transition-transform duration-150 ease-in-out ml-1">
                        →
                    </span>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</Section>
